comments.content: Looks like [Impact](http://web.archive.org/web/20150417093334/http:/www.identifont.com/show?OZ) by Geoffrey Lee and [Heliotype](http://web.archive.org/web/20150417093334/http:/www.identifont.com/show?2WK) by Lee Martin McAuley.
